title: Sandy Maendly
text:
Sandy Maendly is a <a href="Switzerland">Swiss</a> <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>, currently playing for <a href="Servette%20FC%20Ch%C3%AAnois%20F%C3%A9minin">Servette Chênois</a> in <a href="Swiss%20Challenge%20League">Swiss Challenge League</a>. She previously played for <a href="A.S.D.%20AGSM%20Verona%20F.C.">AGSM Verona</a> and <a href="Torres%20Calcio%20Femminile">Torres CF</a> in <a href="Italy">Italy</a>'s <a href="Serie%20A">Serie A</a> and for <a href="YB%20Frauen">YB Frauen</a> and <a href="Servette%20FC%20Ch%C3%AAnois%20F%C3%A9minin">Servette Chênois</a> in Switzerland's <a href="Nationalliga%20A%20%28women%27s%20football%29">Nationalliga A</a>.
She is a member of the <a href="Switzerland%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Swiss national team</a>.
